Z.J.M., Appellant,
v.
C.E.M., Respondent. No. ED 106690 Missouri Court of Appeals, Eastern District, DIVISION FOUR. Filed: July 23, 2019 Jesse A. Granneman, 20 Manor Drive, Troy, MO 63379, for appellant. Michelle M. Funkenbusch, 2901 Dougherty Ferry Rd, Ste. 100, St. Louis, MO 63122, for respondent. Before: Kurt S. Odenwald, P.J., Gary M. Gaertner, Jr., J., and Colleen Dolan, J.

ORDER

PER CURIAM.

Z.J.M. appeals the judgment of the trial court determining paternity, child custody, and child support for a minor child. An extended opinion would have no precedential value. The parties have been provided with a memorandum for their information only, setting forth the reasons for this order. The judgment is affirmed. Rule 84.16(b).
